text: Leonardo DiCaprio and blond model Nina Agdal have called it quits. Sources tell Page Six that the Oscar winner and Victoria ’ s Secret model broke up earlier this week, after dating for nearly a year. But the breakup is amicable. “ They split up early this week and they remain friends, ” said a pal close to the couple. A source added that the relationship “ ran its course. ” They were together in late March for her 25th birthday on a yacht in St. Bart ’ s with pals, including Orlando Bloom. But last Tuesday, the couple was seen at West Hollywood sushi restaurant Itacho, sources tell Page Six, where it seemed that the thrill was gone. Witnesses said that PDA was “ minimal. ” But Agdal doesn ’ t seem too broken up
